Name: %^CYAN%^Cantrips%^RESET%^
Type: Permanent
Prerequisites: Bard, Cleric, Druid, Inquisitor, Mage, Magus, Oracle, Sorcerer

Certain classes learn a variety of useful, but simple spells as part of their rudimentary training. These spells are called %^CYAN%^Cantrips%^RESET%^.

These spells require very little effort or concentration to cast and can be cast at will by the caster.

You can see your cantrip spells by typing 'recall cantrip spells'. 

You can cast your cantrips by typing 'cast cantrip <name>'.

